  "detailed_description": "<h1>关注我们</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《KunKun dream Startles the Soul》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a multiplayer online horror and funny game, the game supports 1~4 people to play. Escape the KunKun’s Dreamscape with your friends in an experimental dream full of ghosts and animals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/e7ba9c7e80d8e3cf5508aabd8f8f5724.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Background of the story》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day when you surf your mobile phone on the Internet, you accidentally brush a kind of Kunkun graphic virus, the human eye will fall asleep when you see the graphic virus, and when you wake up, you arrive at a place that is both familiar and unfamiliar, and you also meet a companion who is trapped here, this place is full of scary and funny ghost animals, echoing in the corridor of the rooster crow, uneasy atmosphere. Can you escape from this \"KunKun’s Dreamscape\"?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/7690a2b87233d3b9160741d69c987cab.poster.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/7690a2b87233d3b9160741d69c987cab.webm?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/7690a2b87233d3b9160741d69c987cab.mp4?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/863aa0b13d6b129369d855463680bdb2.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Gameplay》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the illusory dream, obtain items and information, solve puzzles, and hunt down ghosts and animals. Team up with your teammates to explore the environment for clues, collect key items, and solve the mysteries hidden in KunKun’s Dreamscape one by one, and finally piece together the truth behind them!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/de1b3b93c641a49c812babab52d8a9a9.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=325 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Online multiplayer》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports up to 1~4 people to play in a team, and the challenge is to escape from the \"KunKun’s Dreamscape\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divide up the work to explore, fight for hideouts, and enjoy multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/be2cb71c2170c24f9a4bc1fc97ad9f0c.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=316 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/674bddedb18be47a50576f22b6cb33ae.poster.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/674bddedb18be47a50576f22b6cb33ae.webm?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/674bddedb18be47a50576f22b6cb33ae.mp4?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Multiple maps》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game currently has five maps where you have to face off against ghost animals: KunKun melon buyer Brother Jie They pose a threat to you but are also hilarious and scary! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/ea0c68ce1f5523da5be58f9c60d4725d.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=344 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/2225a4a4795be6bb601da0062f1dd509.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/c7d0662b6d55e92fe0560eacdad1fde8.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Lao Da Beverage》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, you can look for key power-ups: Lao Da Beverage, which will help you increase your running speed and stamina, and the Prison Drink, which will give you a lot of energy! Miss you, Laoda!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/eba3ac93a92470765d5d411009321a61.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=266 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/0ead90b5980fcfd31f589f359d0b350f.poster.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/0ead90b5980fcfd31f589f359d0b350f.webm?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/0ead90b5980fcfd31f589f359d0b350f.mp4?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Anxiolytics》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One more look will explode, and a little closer will melt! In this strange and familiar place, you will inevitably feel nervous and anxious, and when the sin plant reaches a certain level, you will feel dizzy, and you need to take anti-anxiety medicine at this time! to alleviate anxiety symptoms<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/be71d89019d727aa4bf681257260e502.poster.avif?t=1771774892\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/be71d89019d727aa4bf681257260e502.webm?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/be71d89019d727aa4bf681257260e502.mp4?t=1771774892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Game Features》</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape from Grotsque Object</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid and escape before they are caught ,Hide through the cabinets, dark places, toilets! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/644f22b868b8cbd12f09f4a806db0639.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/96552309984e54831bfbb82411e7915a.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=324 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/0a3180647a3cda886fe5f973c1f343f6.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=420 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Solve puzzles together》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the items and information you can find, solve the puzzles of the mechanism</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/38e92fc1018490380762134b860c0edc.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/01c941b1290f3c265e4fd6004605928e.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/4c50aa287e87c60db1dfa42b5853d076.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Collaborative exploration》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the environment for clues, find key items, escape one by one, and unravel the truth behind the mystery hidden in the horror of KunKun’s Dreamscape</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/f7c31cdf4e987ce34f243fbd476ee445.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/54625a69eafbc213038f03d1c2227f49.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=322 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/54bef3c1d7dbe15ade84879458f135d0.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Double ending》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions and actions in the game will determine the outcome, resulting in two possible endings waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808570/extras/48959b0a647022cecfdd7ccc448712a5.avif?t=1771774892\" width=600 height=286 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Note: The characters, locations, and elements involved in the game are purely fictitious and are coincidental if they are similar.</h2>",
